    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 a dependable choice for buyers seeking everyday transportation at a reasonable price. The car starts and runs consistently, handling daily commutes and routine errands without issue. There are visible signs of wear both inside and out, including minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and some wear on the interior surfaces, all consistent with a vehicle that has seen regular use. Mechanically, it performs reliably for its age, though buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or minor repairs may be needed down the road. Overall, this is a practical, honest option for someone who wants transportation without the premium price tag.",
