    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, reliable car that strikes a solid balance between value and quality. The exterior presents nicely with only minor surface imperfections consistent with normal everyday use; no significant dents, deep scratches, or rust to report. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from the overall experience. Mechanically, the car runs and drives confidently \u2014 all major systems are functioning properly, and it has been kept up with routine maintenance. This is an honest, dependable used car that doesn't need any immediate work and is ready to serve its next owner without surprises. A great choice for buyers seeking a quality vehicle at a fair price point.",
